ProductDB
          The ProductDB class encapsulates the list of all products sold in the store.
ProductInfo
          The ProductInfo interface is implemented by any class which represents a saleable product in our store.
SelfCheckOut.checkOutState
          This enumeration represents the four states of the SelfCheckOut system:
READY means the system is awaiting a new customer
ADDING means the system is prepared for another item to be added
BAGGING means the system is awaiting notification that the item has been placed in the bagging area
DONEADDING means the system is waiting for the customer to pay for their items.
Attempts to add items while BAGGING or DONEADDING result in errors.
UPC
          The UPC class represents a Universal Product Code, a unique 12-digit code found on most packaged products.
